snippet.title: SLIME MASTER!! (Slime Rancher #3)
snippet.description:
Today we're expanding out ranch and getting more slimes on Slime Rancher, episode 3 with Typical Gamer! 
► Subscribe for MORE Slime Rancher! ► http://bit.ly/SubToTG
► Previous video! ► https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FuwuvZaTW-4&index=1&list=PLF12pDRgJ2PY771PdZKHp7J-4MXX_U0gv

Description of Slime Rancher on Steam: "Slime Rancher is the tale of Beatrix LeBeau, a plucky, young rancher who sets out for a life a thousand light years away from Earth on the ‘Far, Far Range’ where she tries her hand at making a living wrangling slimes. With a can-do attitude, plenty of grit, and her trusty vacpack, Beatrix attempts to stake a claim, amass a fortune, and avoid the continual peril that looms from the rolling, jiggling avalanche of slimes around every corner."
